Problem Statement

Design a Blackjack simulation with multiple tables, each it's own thread, where variables, such as the probabilities of the
deck are able to be manipulated. A Map would be used to store players and the table they are playing at. The User will act
as a "Manager" of the Simulation/Casino.

Feature List:
User/ManagerOptions
Weighting the Deck
Kicking Players Out
Loaning Money
Move Dealers
Be EVIL
Change Table Color